    "SSO shows competitive performance as compared with a number of state-of-the-art search algorithms for tackling diverse numerical optimization problems.",
    "Besides the above, there are also other swarm intelligence algorithms developed for handling feature selection, hyperparameter search, deep neural architecture generation with respect to image segmentation/classification [19,[39][40][41], human action recognition [42] and environmental sound classification [18], as well as solving other engineering and mathematical optimization problems [43][44][45][46][47][48][49].3 The proposed methods for deepfake detectionThe proposed deepfake detection system consists of three key steps, i.e.",
